{"tid":1656199,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"<抗暴之戰>留言侮辱中大生，黑警跑手同贊助商終止合約","createTime":"2019-10-15T12:57:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-16T07:18:34.000Z","uid":219031,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"55faabab646996acb7955d99d3901bc27a3e1ae1","tid":1656199,"uid":219031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T12:57:33.000Z","msg":"早前有疑似警員在網上發表侮辱大學生言論，同為業餘跑手的他被披露受到運動品牌Asics贊助。有網民到Asics社交網站專頁留言，冀該品牌正視事件。Asics今日公佈，與疑為該名警員的易嘉麟已終止贊助協議。<br />\n<br />\n日前在網上流傳一張社交網站截圖，消息指一位外號為「忌廉」的跑手指「啲中大生真係好吹得。個直播令人想笑。拘捕後被性暴？唔去驗傷？痴」疑為警員易嘉麟的帳號則留言「做天使做到shot（應該為short）左（咗）」，侮辱受害人。事後有網民指，易嘉麟為Asics贊助的跑手，有網民就到Asics社交平台專頁，要求該品牌交代。Asics今日指，易嘉麟已主動提出解除贊助協議，並已經生效。<br />\n<br />\n據長跑界消息人士指，易嘉麟乃香港警隊中特別任務連成員，並沒有在前線參與處理示威的職務，但多次在網上發表侮辱示威者言論，引起多人不滿。據悉Asics一直考慮解決事件的方法，最後易嘉麟主動提出終止合作。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/10/15/205646_d1f0f2d5cb33962108a9efe5bd853415.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F10%2F15%2F205646_d1f0f2d5cb33962108a9efe5bd853415.png&h=eacbc090&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n易嘉麟，SDU<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20191015&amp;s=7032049&amp;a=60157295\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20191015%26s%3D7032049%26a%3D60157295&d=uOCBXhtcaqxtHROYLuBCLHdxOOSMRKapPz%2BIyyZ8sYw%3D&h=43f1fb16\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20191015%26s%3D7032049%26a%3D60157295&h=da3f96cb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20191015&amp;s=7032049&amp;a=60157295</a>"},{"pid":"41ee617dcd9f6291f2d1826ab96ac3ef713b2bf1","tid":1656199,"uid":160592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T12:59:36.000Z","msg":"要支持下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid"